The '''Frozen Ocean of [[Polus]]''' was the only [[Ocean/Legends|ocean]] on the ice [[Planet/Legends|planet]] Polus. Its surface was entirely iced over, but beneath the surface, the bulk of [[Water/Legends|water]] remained liquid, supporting many [[Species/Legends|species]] of aquatic life.

